title: Packed with good actors
review: Good movie for a sundaymorning! Packed with good actors and a good storieline

title: So much going on so little Brain to comprehend it!
review: As a action you want the brainless scenes where a lot of stuff is going on but you keep up! In this.... you need a migraine pill! It's 2.23 hours maximum action with a freaking dialogue!!! Don't get me wrong, I kind of liked it but now and then I realized I had no clue what's going on in the story and how they actually ended up in another fight in another kingdom under water... or on land...
